FBIS3-10857 "drlat049_o_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 Colombia Top Cali Cartel Leader Reportedly Surrenders PA1203155894 Hamburg DPA in Spanish 1528 GMT 12 Mar 94 PA1203155894 Hamburg DPA Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Santa Fe de Bogota, 12 Mar (DPA) -- Julio Fabio Urdinola, a top leader of the Cali cocaine cartel, surrendered to Colombian authorities today, according to Radio Caracol, a private station in Bogota. The report indicates that Urdinola surrendered to a prosecutor in the western city of Palmira. Also surrendering were Hector Porras and Ancizar Ardila, who were sought by Colombian authorities on drug trafficking charges.
